  <p>This dialog offers the configuration of several interface related aspects.</p>
  <section id="settings">
    <title>Settings</title>
    <terms>
      <title>Main</title>
      <item>
        <title>Hide on close</title>
        <p>If you enable this option, GMPC's main window will be minimized instead of closed when requested. If the tray icon is shown, GMPC will hide it's main window.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title>Stylize album covers</title>
