      </item>
      <item>
        <title>Stop playing on exit</title>
        <p>If this option is enabled, GMPC will stop playback before quitting.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title>Show songlist tooltip</title>
        <p>Enable this, if you want tooltips showing further information when hovering items in songlists.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title>Show buttons instead of dropdown in collapsed view</title>
        <p>When enabled, this will show buttons instead of a dropdown to switch between the different browsers in collapsed view.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <title>Enable search as you type. (Might be slow)</title>
        <p>You don't have to press enter to search.</p>
      </item>
    </terms>
    <terms>
      <title>Playlist:</title>
      <item>
        <title>Center playing song</title>
        <p>The currently playing song will be centered in the "Play Queue" browser by automatically scrolling the playlist when the song changes.</p>
